### ========================================
### PRUEBAS EN PRODUCCIÓN - RENDER
### ========================================

### 1. Health Check
GET https://drogueria-bellavista-api.onrender.com/api/actuator/health

### 2. Registrar nuevo usuario
POST https://drogueria-bellavista-api.onrender.com/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@drogueria.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "Bellavista"
}

### 3. Login
POST https://drogueria-bellavista-api.onrender.com/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ========================================
### ENDPOINTS PROTEGIDOS (requieren token)
### Copia el token del login y reemplaza <TOKEN>
### ========================================

### 4. Listar productos
GET https://drogueria-bellavista-api.onrender.com/api/products
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### 5. Crear producto
POST https://drogueria-bellavista-api.onrender.com/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

{
  "code": "PROD-001",
  "name": "Acetaminofén 500mg",
  "description": "Analgésico y antipirético",
  "price": 5000.00,
  "stock": 100,
  "minStock": 10,
  "category": "Medicamentos"
}

### 6. Listar clientes
GET https://drogueria-bellavista-api.onrender.com/api/customers
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### 7. Listar proveedores
GET https://drogueria-bellavista-api.onrender.com/api/suppliers
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### 8. Listar órdenes
GET https://drogueria-bellavista-api.onrender.com/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>